#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.108"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.108:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.108:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga"
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.108:0.3"
msgid "108. Tikicchakasutta"
msgstr "108. Doctors"

# See http://easyayurveda.com/2014/10/10/virechana-therapy-right-method-side-effects-management/
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.218"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tikicchakā, bhikkhave, virecanaṃ denti pittasamuṭṭhānānampi ābādhānaṃ "
"paṭighātāya, semhasamuṭṭhānānampi ābādhānaṃ paṭighātāya, vātasamuṭṭhānānampi "
"ābādhānaṃ paṭighātāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, doctors prescribe a purgative for eliminating illnesses "
"stemming from disorders of bile, phlegm, and wind."

msgctxt "an10.108:1.2"
msgid "Atthetaṃ, bhikkhave, virecanaṃ; ‘netaṃ natthī’ti vadāmi."
msgstr "There is such a purgative, I don’t deny it."

msgctxt "an10.108:1.3"
msgid "Tañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, virecanaṃ sampajjatipi vipajjatipi."
msgstr "But this kind of purgative sometimes works and sometimes fails."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ahañca kho, bhikkhave, ariyaṃ virecanaṃ desessāmi, yaṃ virecanaṃ "
"sampajjatiyeva no vipajjati, yaṃ virecanaṃ āgamma jātidhammā sattā jātiyā "
"parimuccanti, jarādhammā sattā jarāya parimuccanti, maraṇadhammā sattā "
"maraṇena parimuccanti, sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā sattā "
"sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsehi parimuccanti."
msgstr ""
"I will teach a noble purgative that works without fail. Relying on that "
"purgative, sentient beings who are liable to rebirth, old age, and death, to "
"sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress are freed from all these "
"things."

msgctxt "an10.108:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "an10.108:2.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "an10.108:2.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamañca taṃ, bhikkhave, ariyaṃ virecanaṃ, yaṃ virecanaṃ sampajjatiyeva no "
"vipajjati, yaṃ virecanaṃ āgamma jātidhammā sattā jātiyā parimuccanti, "
"jarādhammā sattā jarāya parimuccanti, maraṇadhammā sattā maraṇena "
"parimuccanti, sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā sattā "
"sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsehi parimuccanti?"
msgstr "“And what is the noble purgative that works without fail?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:4.1"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhikassa, bhikkhave, micchādiṭṭhi virittā hoti;"
msgstr "For one of right view, wrong view is purged."

msgctxt "an10.108:4.2"
msgid ""
"ye ca micchādiṭṭhipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa "
"virittā honti;"
msgstr ""
"And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong view are purged."

msgctxt "an10.108:4.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti."
msgstr "And because of right view, many skillful qualities are fully developed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.219"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:5.1"
msgid "Sammāsaṅkappassa, bhikkhave, micchāsaṅkappo viritto hoti … pe …"
msgstr "For one of right thought, wrong thought is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.2"
msgid "sammāvācassa, bhikkhave, micchāvācā virittā hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right speech, wrong speech is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.3"
msgid "sammākammantassa, bhikkhave, micchākammanto viritto hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right action, wrong action is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.4"
msgid "sammāājīvassa, bhikkhave, micchāājīvo viritto hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right livelihood, wrong livelihood is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.5"
msgid "sammāvāyāmassa, bhikkhave, micchāvāyāmo viritto hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right effort, wrong effort is purged."

msgctxt "an10.108:5.6"
msgid "sammāsatissa, bhikkhave, micchāsati virittā hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right mindfulness, wrong mindfulness is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.7"
msgid "sammāsamādhissa, bhikkhave, micchāsamādhi viritto hoti …"
msgstr "For one of right immersion, wrong immersion is purged. …"

msgctxt "an10.108:5.8"
msgid "sammāñāṇissa, bhikkhave, micchāñāṇaṃ virittaṃ hoti … pe …."
msgstr "For one of right knowledge, wrong knowledge is purged. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.108:6.1"
msgid "Sammāvimuttissa, bhikkhave, micchāvimutti virittā hoti;"
msgstr "For one of right freedom, wrong freedom is purged."

msgctxt "an10.108:6.2"
msgid ""
"ye ca micchāvimuttipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa "
"virittā honti;"
msgstr ""
"And the many bad, unskillful qualities produced by wrong freedom are purged."

msgctxt "an10.108:6.3"
msgid "sammāvimuttipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"And because of right freedom, many skillful qualities are fully developed."

msgctxt "an10.108:6.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ kho taṃ, bhikkhave, ariyaṃ virecanaṃ yaṃ virecanaṃ sampajjatiyeva no "
"vipajjati, yaṃ virecanaṃ āgamma jātidhammā sattā jātiyā parimuccanti … pe … "
"sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsehi parimuccantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the noble purgative that works without fail. Relying on this "
"purgative, sentient beings who are liable to rebirth, old age, and death, to "
"sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress are freed from all these "
"things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.108:6.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
